<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٤٧-<span class="c5"> أَخْبَرَنِي عِصْمَةُ بْنُ عِصَامٍ حَدَّثَنَا حَنْبَلٌ أَنَّ أَبَا عَبْدِ اللَّهِ قِيلَ لَهُ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">⦗٥٧⦘ الرَّجُلُ يُوقِفُ عَلَى وَلَدِهِ وَأَهْلِ بَيْتِهِ وَيَقُولُ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>إِنْ وُلِدَ <span class="c4">[لِي]</span> وَلَدٌ فَهُوَ دَاخِلٌ فِي الْوَقْفِ؟<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> جائز.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>